---
// Expertise.astro
---

<section class="py-section-gap-lg bg-white overflow-hidden relative" id="expertise">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter relative">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative">
        <div class="relative rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_80px_-20px_rgba(29,48,97,0.2)]">
          <img class="w-full h-auto object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCuMNCm4cKoMHLMfkh8QdYw80Uk4LOw3aznRQi-vKrPTgUuZ2HJGcaOHwMW_F3NgzLSBNpJI1Bz2R_8S8tRvxA8YTSLodiS9Gs7824iNiMpRipSHpH4vSPJgBOQtN9_6qnzbx9UBk_3DibMfKNjmOzxcD2seOvoVmQF9hMSARadJSYBU8JTjs_qIoYBB_5tXaYjDDBuAgaYXerhr_tl20MhGHJxLH-UfviROr9GJdKvgZTJSO2HZR65Vor0-vZ3HE86a8fuJGMk9hI" alt="Notre expertise terrain" />
          <!-- Overlay badge -->
          <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 bg-primary text-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[280px] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md bg-opacity-95">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 font-display">30+ ans</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-80 font-medium font-sans">D'expertise terrain en conseil paie & social</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative element behind image -->
        <div class="absolute -z-10 -top-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-accent-pink-light rounded-full opacity-50 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -z-10 -bottom-10 -right-10 w-60 h-60 bg-primary-fixed/30 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-10">
        <div class="inline-block px-5 py-2 bg-accent-pink-light text-secondary rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">
          Notre ADN
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary tracking-tight leading-tight font-display">Le Conseil au cœur de la technologie</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-sans">
          L'IA ne remplace pas l'expertise, elle l'augmente. Chez Fiabilis, nos outils sont conçus par des consultants pour des consultants.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-fixed/40 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">groups</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-primary mb-2 font-display">Synergie Humain-Machine</h4>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm font-sans">Nos consultants valident chaque insight généré par l'IA pour garantir une précision absolue.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-fixed/40 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">security_update_good</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-primary mb-2 font-display">Protection des Données</h4>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm font-sans">Sécurité de niveau bancaire. Vos données sociales sont cryptées et hébergées exclusivement en France.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-6">
          <button class="border-2 border-primary text-primary px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-base hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">En savoir plus sur notre méthodologie</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
